"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:36:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他們又覺得悶，要擠進唐人街或回中國體驗那種喧噪和傾軋的危險生活。基因不能適應坦蕩、釋然，直到死了之後，面部肌肉Relax下來的遺容。<br />\n真係好撚低賤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我最有感受就係佢呢段，其實班老一輩香港人都係，成日話移左民悶，成日想過返油尖旺嗰種生活，真係犯賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1924a607f977c5880030588e1335b630b2401c","tid":383121,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0195a104fa28043b2920ad14d930a816efb9242","tid":383121,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:15:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哈利路亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b8e08ecf24356231a7eeca6fbdaf96020d240210","tid":383121,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae57feced377a1c78b8f1f6895ddd301cc30bdbf","tid":383121,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:18:26.000Z","msg":"唔pish唔係人"},{"pid":"4a5d123179531a3fbee1194e4139d5d0bbbc6622","tid":383121,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6867c5b6d1f9feaaadd33c958b727cbd575a90db","tid":383121,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T13:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f303c260059327fabc6886b84a715cdf5d4389e2","tid":383121,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c805c2bc8fb5ac41e5b7ab2bb377251109ae0151","tid":383121,"uid":128261,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:43:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>他們又覺得悶，要擠進唐人街或回中國體驗那種喧噪和傾軋的危險生活。基因不能適應坦蕩、釋然，直到死了之後，面部肌肉Relax下來的遺容。<br />\n真係好撚低賤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我最有感受就係佢呢段，其實班老一輩香港人都係，成日話移左民悶，成日想過返油尖旺嗰種生活，真係犯賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為支那文化只講求物慾，完全缺乏對心靈、文化、美同精神滿足既追求<br />\n香港老一代人去到外國只係貪圖外國物質生活同福利"},{"pid":"a36215afded802ef921c069d997b4ae053b109fb","tid":383121,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T22:25:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"127c9daf45bfe501bc3461d212738cdde4b29d8e","tid":383121,"uid":5007,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T22:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://kagaminerin.org/hongkong/src/1384257509308.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkagaminerin.org%2Fhongkong%2Fsrc%2F1384257509308.jpg&h=45230c17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8dd9f21291bce911af4a93276801a7115862cd35","tid":383121,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T00:41:16.000Z","msg":"Pish"}]}